Docs.summary:
Represents a hash set that mutates with little or no memory allocations and that can produce or build on immutable hash set instances very efficiently.
**NuGet package**: System.Collections.Immutable (about immutable collections and how to install)

remarks.format: ## Remarks Although <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Union%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and other methods already provide fast bulk change operations on a collection, the <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Builder> class allows multiple combinations of changes to be made to a set with equal efficiency.
